---
title: Haloumi & Chipotle Mayo Burger with Spiced Kumara Fries & Beetroot Relish
description: This squeaky burger gets a big "yes, please!" from all of our recipe testers, and for good reason. With tangy beetroot relish, smokey mild chipotle mayo and a fresh touch from tomato and salad leaves, every bite is a true delight.
